{
  "texts": [
    "Reversible blocks enable models with limited memory to be larger.",
    "ViT can be utilized in Explainable AI 33 to provide insight into how an image classification decision is made.",
    "By using attention maps generated by ViT, it is possible to visualize which aspects of an image are most crucial to the classification decision.",
    "This information can be used to clarify the model's decision when communicating with humans.",
    "In Table 1, the article summarizes recent contributions made for a range of tasks using Vision Transformer architecture."
